metadata.name: The Queen of Dragons
metadata.description: "The Queen of Dragons," a gift from me to you, a mighty force to be reckoned with. Her fire burns bright, illuminating all within her reach she commands respect and admiration from all who know her. She is a fierce protector, always standing up for what is right and just. And in times of crisis, she is a beacon of hope, leading the way towards a brighter future.
